  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[How to dpm in Drupal 8]]></title>
    <link href="http://drupal8notes.github.io/how-to-dpm-in-drupal-8/"/>
    <updated>2014-11-05T00:19:22-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://drupal8notes.github.io/how-to-dpm-in-drupal-8</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Looks like <code>dpm()</code> is broken right now in devel. It gives you a WSOD.</p>

<p>Here&rsquo;s some alternatives with the devel module enabled:</p>

<h4>1. Krumo</h4>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='php'><span class='line'><span class="nx">krumo</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$variables</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>2. Kint</h4>

<p><a href="http://raveren.github.io/kint/">Kint</a> is a great alternative to Krumo.</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='php'><span class='line'><span class="nx">kint</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$variables</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>2. Dump for Twig</h4>

<p>Inside Twig template you can:</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>{{ dump() }}</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
